item.title: About
item.description: Hi, I’m Daniel Ting! Welcome to Super Pork Chop, my blog. As a senior worker bee in a distant land of fire and ice, I teach young roombas the errors of their ways, so they may one day be released into the wild. My interests lie in computer security, embedded systems programming, and emacs, and I’m frequently attracted to the new and shiny. These posts are a rambling collection of things that I’ve learned, and I hope you’ll learn something new as well.
